@page
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About CoinTrade";
}



<div style="margin-top: 30px;">
    <h2>Welcome to CoinTrade</h2>
    <p>
        Welcome to CoinTrade, a cutting-edge cryptocurrency trading simulator developed by Erik Moren, Gustav Holmström, and Amir Hebib as part of our school project.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
        Our mission is to provide a realistic and engaging platform for users to practice cryptocurrency trading without the risk of losing real money. Whether you're a novice looking to understand the basics of crypto trading or an experienced trader wanting to test strategies, CoinTrade offers a safe and educational environment to hone your skills.
    </p>

    <h2>What is CoinTrade?</h2>
    <p>
        CoinTrade is a trading simulator where users can buy and sell various cryptocurrencies, leveraging realistic market data to maximize their virtual wealth. Starting with a set amount of virtual currency, users can track real-time market prices via an API and make informed trading decisions. The game is designed to mimic the actual trading experience as closely as possible, allowing users to learn and practice before venturing into real markets.
    </p>

    <h2>Features</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>User Registration and Login:</strong> Create an account to save your progress and track your trading history.</li>
        <li><strong>Real-Time Market Data:</strong> Stay updated with real-time cryptocurrency prices fetched through a public API.</li>
        <li><strong>Trade Simulation:</strong> Buy and sell cryptocurrencies with virtual money. Experiment with leverage to maximize potential gains (or losses).</li>
        <li><strong>Balance and Portfolio Overview:</strong> Keep an eye on your virtual portfolio and balance, making informed decisions based on your performance.</li>
        <li><strong>Trading History:</strong> Review your past trades to analyze your strategy and learn from your successes and mistakes.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Why CoinTrade?</h2>
    <p>
        CoinTrade is not just a game; it's an educational tool designed to bridge the gap between theoretical knowledge and practical experience in cryptocurrency trading. By simulating real-world trading scenarios, we aim to prepare users for the volatile and exciting world of cryptocurrencies.
    </p>

    <h2>Join Us</h2>
    <p>
        Dive into the world of cryptocurrency trading with CoinTrade. Learn, practice, and become a better trader without any financial risk. Your journey to mastering crypto trading starts here!
    </p>
</div>
